    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h1>Programme Placement</h1>

      <p>Children are placed into programmes according to their ages as of September 1* of the year of enrolment.</p>
      <p>* In the case of students born in September the school will decide to which grade level they are admitted, based on documentation as well as the results of a trial day and, possibly, testing.</p>

